''' Iskender bogazi dardir gecilmez'''([[:tr:İskender Boğazı Dardır Geçilmez|tr]])<ref>{{cite web|title=www.edebiyatvesanatakademisi.com|url=http://www.edebiyatvesanatakademisi.com/i-i-ile-baslayanlar/iskender-bogazi-dardir-gecilmez-1-31194.aspx|accessdate=16 December 2016}}</ref> or '''Φίλα με γιατί λειώνω''' ([[:el:Φίλα με γιατί λειώνω|el]]) is a Turkish and Greek folkloric tune ([[Karsilamas]]).The meter is {{music|time|9|8}}.Its Turkish music was composed (Kemani Serkis Efendi)([[Sarkis Suciyan]]).<ref>{{cite news|title=KEMANİ SERKİS EFENDİ -Karcığar-İskender Boğazı dardır geçilmez|url=http://eksd.org.tr/bestecilerimiz/kemani_serkis_efendi/karcigar_iskender_bogazi_dardir_ge%C3%A7ilmez.pdf|accessdate=16 December 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=TRT|url=http://bizdenezgiler.com/#!/eserler/besteci/kemani_serkis_efendi|accessdate=16 December 2016}}</ref> Its Greek lyrics written by [[Stelios Chrysinis]].<ref>{{cite web|title=φιλα με γιατι λιωνω - Rebetiko Online.|url=http://www.rebetiko.gr/tragoudia.php?song_id=20005913|accessdate=18 December 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Περιγραφή: Φίλα με για να με λιώσεις|url=http://libsearch.teiep.gr/Record/1%2F34266|accessdate=18 December 2016}}</ref> ==[[Agapios Tomboulis]] versions== Ισκεντέρ Μπογάζι(κιοτσέκικο = [[köçek]])(İskender Boğazı dardırgeçilmez/ Ben yarimi gördüm)(Years 1930)<ref>{{cite web|title=http://www.recordingpioneers.com:Ισκεντέρ Μπογάζι (κιοτσέκικο = köçek) (İskender Boğazı dardır geçilmez/ Ben yarimi gördüm)|url=http://www.recordingpioneers.com/grurks/images/pdf/TOMBOULIS-EN.pdf|accessdate=18 February 2017}}</ref>
==Original form== The original form of the karsilamas was popular in [[İzmir]].<ref>{{cite web|title=turkuyurdu|url=http://www.turkuyurdu.com/turku-notalari/iskender-bogazi-dardir-gecilmez-11721.htm|accessdate=16 December 2016}}</ref>
