'''William Guillén Padilla''' (born April 26, 1963) is a [[Peru]]vian [[poet]] and [[Storytelling|storyteller]].<ref>http://www.librosperuanos.com/autores/autor/3543/Guillen-Padilla-William</ref> He excels in the genre of literary [[Flash fiction|minifiction]].<ref name="blogspot">{{cite web|url=http://eltonhonores.blogspot.com/2012/09/presentacion-de-microcuentos-de-william.html|title=Iluminaciones: Presentación de Microcuentos de William Guillén por José Hidalgo|publisher=eltonhonores.blogspot.com|accessdate=2014-08-11}}</ref><ref name="blogspot2">{{cite web|url=http://eltonhonores.blogspot.com/2012/02/william-guillen-padilla-cuaderno-de.html|title=Iluminaciones: William Guillén Padilla. Cuaderno de almanaquero. Cajamarca: Municipalidad Provincial de Cajamarca, 2011. 482 pp.|publisher=eltonhonores.blogspot.com|accessdate=2014-08-11}}</ref>
